---
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <Nav />
  <div class="left-column">
    <Card icon="fa-solid fa-code" title="Frontend Development" />
    <Card icon="fa-solid fa-paint-brush" title="Web Development" />
    <Card icon="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen" title="Mobile App Development" />
  </div>

  <div class="right-column">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <p>
      I've spent the last few years working as a Front end Developer, building
      websites and products that are intuitive, accessible, and enjoyable to
      use. What I enjoy most is bringing designs to life and thinking about the
      people on the other side of the screen. Accessibility is something I care
      deeply about, and I try to consider it throughout the development process
      rather than treating it as an afterthought. I'm also interested in the
      bigger picture of a product: how it supports user needs, how it reflects
      the product I'm building.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
